{
  "texts": [
    "The third row demonstrates how DQA enables the occupancy map to capture a truck that is partially obscured by a fence.",
    "Since the fence obstructs the truck in the image view, its semantic information is not well projected into the 3D space.",
    "However, by leveraging QueryAgg, the model directly aggregates object-level information, allowing the truck to be accurately represented in the occupancy map.",
    "Additionally, Figures 7 to 10 visualize the model's performance in complex scenarios.",
    "Figure 6.6Figure 6."
  ]
}